## 7. Recommendations for V1.0

### Technology Stack (Validated)

| Component | Choice | Rationale |
|-----------|--------|-----------|
| **Renderer** | React Three Fiber 8.x | React 18 compatibility, existing implementation |
| **Helpers** | drei 9.x | Pairs with R3F 8.x |
